{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_017PLSZYFwhNkW9Fhm2Rcj1N","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I now have all the context needed. Here is the complete implementation.\n\n---\n\n## File 1: `api/operator/v1alpha1/istiocsr_types.go`\n\n### Change 1: Add presence-immutability CEL rule to `IstioCSRConfig` type\n\nAdd a CEL validation marker on the `IstioCSRConfig` type (just above the `type IstioCSRConfig struct` line):\n\n```go\n// IstioCSRConfig configures the istio-csr agent's behavior.\n// +kubebuilder:validation:XValidation:rule=\"!has(oldSelf.tlsMinVersion) && !has(self.tlsMinVersion) || has(oldSelf.tlsMinVersion) && has(self.tlsMinVersion)\",message=\"tlsMinVersion may only be configured during creation\"\ntype IstioCSRConfig struct {\n```\n\nThis follows the exact same pattern used on `IstiodTLSConfig` for `privateKeyAlgorithm` and `privateKeySize` (lines 180–181).\n\n### Change 2: Add the `tlsMinVersion` field to `IstioCSRConfig`\n\nInsert this field after the `NodeSelector` field (before the closing brace of `IstioCSRConfig`), at line 157:\n\n```go\n\t// tlsMinVersion is the minimum TLS version for the istio-csr agent's serving certificate.\n\t// Valid values are VersionTLS12 and VersionTLS13.\n\t// This field is immutable once set.\n\t// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum:=\"VersionTLS12\";\"VersionTLS13\"\n\t// +kubebuilder:validation:XValidation:rule=\"oldSelf == '' || self == oldSelf\",message=\"tlsMinVersion is immutable once set\"\n\t// +kubebuilder:validation:Optional\n\t// +optional\n\tTLSMinVersion string `json:\"tlsMinVersion,omitempty\"`\n```\n\n### Full diff for `istiocsr_types.go`\n\nThe `IstioCSRConfig` type should look like this after modification:\n\n```go\n// IstioCSRConfig configures the istio-csr agent's behavior.\n// +kubebuilder:validation:XValidation:rule=\"!has(oldSelf.tlsMinVersion) && !has(self.tlsMinVersion) || has(oldSelf.tlsMinVersion) && has(self.tlsMinVersion)\",mes